<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Rechnung <%= invLabel %> – Propus</title>
  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', system-ui, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 1.5; color: #111; max-width: 210mm; margin: 0 auto; padding: 15mm; }
    @media print { body { padding: 0; } }
    .header { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-start; margin-bottom: 2rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #ccc; padding-bottom: 1rem; }
    .logo img { width: 150px; height: auto; display: block; }
    .meta { text-align: right; font-size: 0.9rem; color: #555; }
    h1 { font-size: 1.3rem; margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0; }
    .invoice-id { font-size: 0.95rem; color: #666; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    .parties { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 2rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    .party { font-size: 0.95rem; }
    .party strong { display: block; margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }
    table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 1.5rem 0; }
    th, td { padding: 0.5rem 0.75rem; text-align: left; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd; }
    th { font-weight: 600; background: #f5f5f5; }
    .amount { text-align: right; font-weight: 600; }
    .footer { margin-top: 2rem; padding-top: 1rem; border-top: 1px solid #ccc; font-size: 0.85rem; color: #666; }
    .no-print { margin-top: 1.5rem; }
    .no-print button, .no-print a { margin-right: 0.5rem; padding: 0.5rem 1rem; cursor: pointer; font-size: 0.9rem; text-decoration: none; border: 1px solid #10b981; border-radius: 6px; background: #10b981; color: #fff; display: inline-block; }
    .no-print a.btn-ghost { background: transparent; color: #10b981; }
    @media print { .no-print { display: none !important; } }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <div class="logo"><img src="https://propus.ch/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Asset-2-2.png" alt="Propus" loading="eager" decoding="async"></div>
    <div class="meta">
      <%= creditor.name %><br>
      <%= creditor.email %><br>
      <%= creditor.website %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h1>Rechnung</h1>
  <div class="invoice-id"><%= invLabel %> · <%= invoiceDate %> · <%= statusLabel %></div>

  <div class="parties">
    <div class="party">
      <strong>Rechnungssteller</strong>
      <%= creditor.name %><br>
      <%= creditorLines[1] %><br>
      <%= creditorLines[2] %><br>
      <%= creditor.email %>
    </div>
    <div class="party">
      <strong>Rechnungsempfänger</strong>
      <%= customerName || '-' %><br>
      <%= customerEmail || '' %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <p><strong>Tour / Objekt:</strong> <%= tourLabel || '-' %></p>
  <% if (tourAddress) { %><p><strong>Adresse:</strong> <%= tourAddress %></p><% } %>
  <% if (tourLink) { %><p><strong>Link:</strong> <a href="<%= tourLink %>" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><%= tourLink %></a></p><% } %>
  <p><strong>Periode:</strong> <%= billingPeriodLabel || '-' %></p>

  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Pos.</th>
        <th>Beschreibung</th>
        <th class="amount">Betrag (CHF)</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td>1</td>
        <td><%= bezeichnung || 'Virtueller Rundgang – Hosting / Verlängerung' %></td>
        <td class="amount"><%= amount %></td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <p style="margin-top: 1.5rem;"><strong>Total: CHF <%= amount %></strong></p>
  <p><strong>QR-Referenz:</strong> <%= qrReferenceFormatted %></p>
  <p><strong>IBAN:</strong> <%= creditorIbanFormatted %></p>

  <div class="footer">
    <p>Vielen Dank für Ihr Vertrauen. Bei Fragen erreichen Sie uns unter <%= creditor.email %>.</p>
    <p>Für den normgerechten QR-Zahlteil bitte den PDF-Download verwenden.</p>
    <p>Freundliche Grüsse<br><%= creditor.name %></p>
  </div>

  <div class="no-print">
    <button type="button" onclick="window.print();">Drucken</button>
    <a href="<%= pdfUrl %>" class="btn-ghost" download>PDF herunterladen</a>
    <a href="/portal/tours/<%= tour.id %>">← Zurück zur Tour</a>
  </div>

  <script>
    if (window.location.search.includes('print=1')) {
      window.onload = function() { window.print(); };
    }
  </script>
</body>
</html>
